headline: Will Tesla Stock Pop or Drop in 2025?
summary: Tesla (NASDAQ: TSLA) has been one of the biggest surprises of 2024.  The company first impressed investors with its third-quarter earnings report, which showed strong profit growth, and CEO Elon Musk predicted that vehicle production would increase by 20% to 30% in 2025, a significant improvement from flat growth in 2024.  Then, Tesla soared following the election as Musk's big bet on Trump seemed to pay off.
